<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Online Examination System</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#7c3aed,#ec4899);
    padding:40px;
}

.container{
    max-width:800px;
    margin:auto;
    background:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:20px;
    box-shadow:0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

h1{
    text-align:center;
    color:#2563eb;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.question{
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.question h3{
    color:#333;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

input[type="submit"]{
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    background:#2563eb;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Online Examination</h1>

<form action="ExamServlet" method="post">

<div class="question">
<h3>1. Which language is used for Servlet programming?</h3>
<input type="radio" name="q1" value="Java"> Java<br>
<input type="radio" name="q1" value="Python"> Python<br>
<input type="radio" name="q1" value="C"> C<br>
</div>

<div class="question">
<h3>2. Which protocol is used on the Web?</h3>
<input type="radio" name="q2" value="FTP"> FTP<br>
<input type="radio" name="q2" value="HTTP"> HTTP<br>
<input type="radio" name="q2" value="SMTP"> SMTP<br>
</div>

<div class="question">
<h3>3. Which tag is used to create a form?</h3>
<input type="radio" name="q3" value="table"> table<br>
<input type="radio" name="q3" value="form"> form<br>
<input type="radio" name="q3" value="body"> body<br>
</div>

<input type="submit" value="Submit Exam">

</form>

</div>

</body>
</html>
